Ask HN: Who would be interested in a browser extension for fast video upscaling?
text:
Just asking, I didn't develop anything yet.

It would allows you to turn a 360p video into a 4k video on the fly for example. It would fill also the black bars in vertical content or if you have a wide display. (Probably with something like stable diffusion)

Do you have any recommendations?

What would be the ideal ux and do you guys have any idea whether this is even possible with current technology?

What amount would you be ready to pay if any?

title: Ask HN: What tool do you use for journaling? Privacy vs. availability tradeoff?
text:
There are a number of search results for threads about journaling ...

..but these days, what do you use for your own ?

I admit I'm a little stuck in between using a cloud service and then being worried about someone reading it one day somehow, and a local .txt type of thing where I have to encrypt and sync it somewhere off the machine. Also, it'd be nice to have phone availability.

I'm curious what others do, or maybe if you're just less paranoid than I am.
